The paper focuses on understanding and predicting image memorability, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of deep learning architectures also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Lastly, the analysis of eye fixations and saliency in relation to image memorability could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
